node.text: Had the amazing opportunity to work with @selenagomez + @rarebeauty on their In My Prime Campaign for the new Always An Optimist Pore Diffusing Primer! I’m so thankful that Selena chose me to capture a couple of friends in their prime all while being in my prime as a photographer which you guys know I’ve been trying to step more in to! It was such a cool moment for my career to combine both beauty and photography 🥺❤️ thank you again @selenagomez x @rarebeauty !!
